net.opentsdb.core

Class HistogramDataPointCodec

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.core.HistogramDataPointCodec
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleHistogramDecoder

    public abstract class HistogramDataPointCodec
extends Object
    Responsible for encoding or decoding HistogramDataPoints to and from byte arrays. NOTE: Implementation of this plugin should be thread safe.
    Since:
    2.4
    See Also:
    HistogramCodecManager
